Package mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.row

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractRowProvider
    This is a simple abstraction on providing the next row to skip for the RowProviderSkippingIterator to act on.
    BasicRowIdStore
    This encapsulates mappings of pixels on a spatially referenced image to/from row IDs.
    CountThresholdRowIdStore
    This extends the concept of the BasicRowIdStore which tracks painted pixels and their mapping to row IDs, but it only marks a pixel (or cell of pixels) as 'painted' once it has exceeded a threshold number of times rendered.
    DecimatedRenderingRowProvider
    This wraps a row ID store as a row provider.
    DecomposedQueryRangeRowProvider
    This class decomposes the given Envelope into a set of Accumulo row ID ranges to use as a row provider to inform seeking to only the given Envelope's decomposed ranges of row IDs.
    ImageDecimator
    This class ties a row ID store to notification events for all pixels that are rendered on an image.
    RowProviderSkippingIterator
    This class wraps a source iterator and a row provider to provide the logic for seeks based on the given row provider to the given source iterator.
